// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2024-1030 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: a9901015-7613-5371-bf1f-273506615598

#event_simpleName=*
| (ImageFileName = *oraclelinux:7* OR ImageFileName = *oraclelinux:8*)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
